                    <span>I read "Shaking the Money Tree" from front to back & immediately went about following many of the author's suggestions for finding funding for my proposed documentary film project on mermaid myths, art & lore around the world!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A valuable book</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>0</span>
                      /
                      <span>0</span>
