                    </div>
                    <span>If you are going to raise funds, you need a well-thought out plan. Novices often waste time and resources learning by trial and error. In SHAKING THE MONEY TREE, Morrie Warshawski offers expert and no-nonsense advice that will be invaluable to filmmakers seeking grants and donations. Mark Litwak, author and entertainment attorney.</span>
                  
              
